item.dc:creator: @teady160 teady160
item.description:
@teady160 wrote:

The soul is right. Instead of clicking the space bar 5 times, use the ‘Tab’ button located left of ‘Q’ on your Keyboard. If you don’t you will get errors because java can’t recognise that type of format.
